nodes.text: Mon Calamari Eye 1 was an abstract painting made sometime after the Battle of Yavin. It was one of two paintings made by Kahfr Oladi that were put on display at the Museum of Tatooine.
Painting of a Mon Calamari Eye 1 was a painting in the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided, prior to the game's closure on December 15, 2011.
